            "text": "563 - "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «لَيْسَ لَكُمْ أَنْ تُعَزُّونَا"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "لَنَا أَنْ نُعَزِّيَكُمْ إِنَّمَا لَكُمْ أَنْ تُهَنِّئُونَا لِأَنَّكُمْ تُشَارِكُونَنَا"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " فِي"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:28:6",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/28/563",
      "text": [
        " اَلْمُصِيبَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.563 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"It is not for you to offer us condolences, but it is for us to offer you condolences. Indeed, it is for you to congratulate us, because you share in our misfortune”."
        ]
      }
    },
